Some songs should be arranged according to their originality. I'm not saying to use only harmonium, tobla or fluit, but songs like Rabindra, Najrul, Polli, folk should be spared from electronic music. In modern song, they can do fusion of EDM...

snippet.textDisplay: From Kanika Banerjee's ,Sreekanta Acharya's ,Rezwana Bonna's ,Jayati Chakrabarty,Arnab's, Audity Muhsin's previous one and then this duet with Bappa Majumdar I am just so in love with this song for a very long time!!!!Can't thank you guys enough for the vibe,the masterpiece that you all have created.And a big salute to all the musicians for their magic to lift up my soul and experience something heavenly!

snippet.textDisplay: Any composition like any design is only beautiful at its simplest form. Each and every composition of Mr. Arnob screams redundancy, unnecessary usage of layers .. that destroys that simplicity that is inherent in the original songs. He should now (that he has brutally murdered the otherwise beautiful songs) understand  the more the merrier does not apply to music/ instrumentals etc. I wish he had lived up to the legacy of Coke studio standards set by Pakistani and Indian music.

snippet.textDisplay:
বাইরে শ্রাবণের বৃষ্টি। রাত তিনটায় এমন ঝুম আউলা বাতাসে গানটা শুনছি।

-গানটি গাওয়া হচ্ছে মালকোষ রাগে। যা ভৌরবী ঠাঠের অঙ্গ। জাত, ঔড়ব-ঔড়ব। এই রাগের অধীনরা- রাগিণী, পুত্র ও পুত্রবধূ।

পুত্র সোম, পরাশনসহ ৫জন। স্ত্রী আশাবরী, সুরঠীসহ ৫ জন। আশাবরী নামটা বেশ চেনা না! 

যাই হোক এই মালকোষ রাগ শোনার সময়- রাত্রি তৃতীয় প্রহর।

ইয়েস এখন রাত্রী তৃতীয় প্রহর।
